Goals 2016
- Setting up an appropriate financial management system- Setting up a business plan


. Goals 2017
- Improving financial management system (Tally training), including follow up on internal control report 2016- Boost internal capitalisation campaign (&amp;gt;50 million UGX)
- Improve knowledge on exporting, to be able to export themselves.
- Improve productivity of member cocoa farms by at least 3% through a sustainable union extension system.</narrative>
